{"tid":1308703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"最佳示範！長沙灣南亞漢揮拳擊倒破壞連儂牆的藍絲","createTime":"2019-07-12T03:13:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T04:14:29.000Z","uid":188721,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"efc2cdf62bec54da5a2da10eb04aa91ed04e800e","tid":1308703,"uid":188721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:13:14.000Z","msg":"型啊！長沙灣南亞漢揮拳擊倒破壞連儂牆的藍絲<br />\n<br />\n昨晚(11日)11時許，有不滿他人藉「連儂牆」表達意見的市民，到港鐵長沙灣站C2出口外的「連儂牆」撕下貼紙，期間一名本地男子，遭一名南亞漢干涉並揮拳擊倒在地。未幾，在場另一名疑「睇唔過眼」的男市民，亦向撕貼紙的男子揮拳，打中其臉部，2名涉嫌施襲者及後趁亂逃離現場，被打男子臉及嘴受傷，送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190712/mobile/bkn-20190712001654157-0712_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190712%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190712001654157-0712_00822_001.html&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0AogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=5ed71e8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190712/mobile/bkn-20190712001654157-0712_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">打得好！拳拳到肉！以後唔會話南亞人係南亞狗！<br />\n真心佩服！請受小弟一拜！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"6c05e78482a4c64f9253fe7f5ccd04b40947f8f7","tid":1308703,"uid":60398,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:36:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">立即停手，我而家嚴重警告你，唔好再襲擊<br />\n<br />\n我而家係制止你再打人，請立即停手<br />\n<br />\n我而家係公民拘捕你，因為你對我朋友施以實質傷害的襲擊</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n然後幾個一齊撲上去<br />\n各位識做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74cd493ad4b3a54d12795cf436ebb5603f6af47d","tid":1308703,"uid":188721,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:39:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Na3x1HP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNa3x1HP.png&h=e16ff1f1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b74986a13